parameters: How could we allow a mere mortal girl to enter?。
If I tell you my name, you're gonna regret it.。
Oh, well, either way, you're doomed to die here.。
So you're the real master of this place, huh?
You seem to want to assume it has something to do with me, but...
It was distorted by the miasma on its own.
The end of the fall of the will-less...
I live off the emotions of human misery.
One of the dark trees, no name.。
It says here, The Great Unholy Tree.。
No matter where we grow our roots, it is human beings themselves who will bring us food.。
I'm not going to go out of my way to manipulate a creature with greed.
You don't have to make them your pawns.。
I know you're at ・・・・・・・・・・・・.。
...there are people like this, aren't there?。
People who think they deserve to exist.。
We all live by helping each other.。
If you have a weakness, I'll support you.
I scold him when he's not doing well.
And you're the one who's getting paid to do it.
There are people crying in the shadows, and you're terrible!
Don't get me wrong, little girl.
I resent you for trying to see things the same way.。
Do you really think you and I are equal?
You're only supposed to let the livestock squeal inside the fence.。
We're outside the fence.。You talk too much, little girl.。
That means I can headbutt you in the ass.。
・・・・・・?　What are you talking about?
For all the times I've wasted on people...
Now it's your turn to cry!
We humans are not your food!
Just go back to the demon world and eat some grass!
・・・・・・・・・ So, humans are not stupid, either.。
Now that we've lost the power to maintain it here, we have no choice but to return to the demon world, but...
Are you sure?　This place is gonna fall apart any second.。
It would be a shame to miss out on eating you.。
Survive as long as you can... human.。
Why does the last boss have to maintain the dungeon by himself!
Sometimes you just have to build it sturdy!
I've just beaten you... Is this how it's going to end again?
If I protect you, you might not be able to escape.。
You've got a bigger role to play.。
Can you help me with something I can't do?
You can do it, right?　Please.。
I can't leave Arles alone. ・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・
Do you want to save it?
I knew you were stronger than I thought.
Don't worry, this is a different dimension.。
But he's human enough to have made it through here.
I'm sure you'll have a great time...
All the senses are concentrated in this sludge.
Let all your emotions drip and fall...
